&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Staff Nurse - Dawlish Hospita&lt;/span&gt;l&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 Staff Nurse at Dawlish Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are compassionate, flexible and have an innovative mind we have an exciting opportunity for you within our team. As a Staff Nurse at Dawlish Community Hospital you will be supporting the day-to-day running of the ward, co-ordinating the clinical care activity and ensuring the provision of a high standard of nursing care, advising and giving information to patients, their families and carers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working alongside our GP&#39;s and Intermediate Care Teams, facilitating patient choice, promoting independence and maintaining patient safety whilst working within your NMC Code of Conduct. The care needs of patients at Dawlish Community Hospital include sub-acute care, Rehabilitation and End of Life care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post offers variety, and the chance to develop your knowledge and skills within a friendly and welcoming team. We will support you in your role, and provide opportunities for ongoing learning and development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
